1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,120
I remember something in it wanted to punish them.

2
00:00:03,120 --> 00:00:06,680
I remember from the moment they moved in, the house was alive.

3
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:09,240
I remember whispers echoed in the halls.

4
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:11,960
I remember windows tapped in the night.

5
00:00:11,960 --> 00:00:13,760
I remember floors creaked.

6
00:00:13,760 --> 00:00:17,360
I remember worst of all was the back room where Cat and Sharon slept.

7
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:19,960
A room their mother always called evil.

8
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:24,280
Sharon, 14 and rebellious fought constantly with their mother.

9
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:27,120
I remember the fights seemed to awaken something.

10
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:32,000
I remember at night Sharon would scream from nightmares, sometimes waking with scratches

11
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:33,480
and bruises.

12
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:38,440
I remember soon Cat, her mother and the other siblings began seeing things, shadows

13
00:00:38,440 --> 00:00:43,360
that didn't belong, figures in corners, eyes that glowed in the dark.

14
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:46,360
I remember the house became a trap of fear and anger.

15
00:00:46,360 --> 00:00:48,800
I remember her mother called a priest for a blessing.
